<doc id="1110997" wikidata="Q353324" url="?curid=1110997" title="Brunner">
<text>Brunner may refer to:

==Places==
* Brunner, New Zealand
* Lake Brunner, New Zealand
* Brunner Mine, New Zealand
* Brunner, Houston, United States
* Brunner (crater), lunar crater

